short_desc: If BLOODAD or CSFAD or FDGAD or TRACERAD or STRUCTAD or BIOMAD1 or BIOMAD2 or BIOMAD3 = 1, ALZDIS should =1
full_desc: If Q3a. BLOODAD (Blood-based biomarkers - Consistent with AD) =1 or Q4a. CSFAD (CSF-based biomarkers - Consistent with AD) =1 or Q6b1. FDGAD (FDG PET - Consistent with AD) =1 or Q6d1. TRACERAD (Other tracer-based imaging - Consistent with AD) =1 or Q7a1. STRUCTAD (Atrophy pattern conistent with AD) =1 or Q8a. BIOMAD1 (Other biomarker modality - Consistent with AD) =1 or Q9a. BIOMAD2 (Other biomarker modality - Consistent with AD) =1 or Q10a. BIOMAD3 (Other biomarker modality - Consistent with AD) =1, then Q12. ALZDIS (Alzheimer's disease) should = 1
test_logic: If (BLOODAD or CSFAD or FDGAD or TRACERAD or STRUCTAD or BIOMAD1 or BIOMAD2 or BIOMAD3) = 1 and ALZDIS not =1
comp_vars: BLOODAD, CSFAD, FDGAD, TRACERAD, STRUCTAD, BIOMAD1, BIOMAD2, BIOMAD3, ALZDIS

full_desc: If Q7a3. STRUCTCVD (Consistent with cerebrovascular disease (CVD)) =1 then Q15. CVD (Vascular brain injury) should = 1

short_desc: If AMYLCSF[UDSv3] or CSFTAU[UDSv3] = 1, then CSFAD should =1
full_desc: If Q6b. AMYLCSF (abnormally low amyloid CSF) or Q6f. CSFTAU (abnormally elevated CSF tau or ptau) at previous visit = 1, then Q4a. CSFAD (CSF-based biomarkers - Consistent with AD) should =1
test_logic: If AMYLCSF[UDSv3] or CSFTAU[UDSv3] = 1 and CSFAD not =1

full_desc: If Q6a. AMYLPET (abnormal amyloid PET) at previous visit = 1, then Q6a1. AMYLPET (Elevated amyloid) should =1
If Q6e. TAUPETAD (Tau PET evidence for AD) at previous visit = 1, then Q6a2. TAUPET (Elevated tau pathology) should =1
If Q6c. FDGAD (FDG-PET pattern of AD) at previous visit = 1, then Q6b1. FDGAD (FDG PET - Consistent with AD should =1
If Q6j. DATSCAN (DATscan) at previous visit = 1, then Q6c. DATSCANDX (Was DAT Scan data or information used to support an etiological diagnosis?) should =1
If Q7a. IMAGLINF (large vessel infarct) at previous visit = 1, then Q7a3a. IMAGLINF (Large vessel infarct(s)) should =1
If Q7c. IMAGMACH (macrohemorrhage) at previous visit = 1, then Q7a3c. IMAGMACH (Macrohemorrhage(s)) should =1
If Q7d.  IMAGMICH (microhemorrhage) at previous visit = 1, then Q7a3d. IMAGMICH (Microhemorrhage(s)) should =1

short_desc: If IMAGMWMH[UDSv3] or IMAGEWMH[UDSv3]  = 1, then IMAGWMH should =1
full_desc: If Q7e. IMAGMWMH (moderate white matter hyperintensities) or Q7f.  IMAGEWMH (extensive white matter hyperintensities) at previous visit = 1, then Q7a3e. IMAGWMH (White-matter hyperintensity) should =1
test_logic: If IMAGMWMH[UDSv3] or IMAGEWMH[UDSv3] = 1 and IMAGWMH not =1

short_desc: If ADMUT[UDSv3]  or FTLDMUT[UDSv3]  or OTHMUT[UDSv3]  = 1, then AUTDOMMUT should =1
full_desc: If Q8. ADMUT (dominantly inherited AD mutation) or Q9. FTLDMUT (dominantly inherited FTLD mutation) or Q10. OTHMUT (hereditary mutation other than an AD or FTLD mutation) at previous visit = 1, then Q11. AUTDOMMUT (Is there an autosomal dominant pathogenic variant to support an etiological diagnosis?) should =1
test_logic: If ADMUT[UDSv3] or FTLDMUT[UDSv3] or OTHMUT[UDSv3] = 1 and AUTDOMMUT not =1

full_desc: If Q7b. IMAGLAC (lacunar infarct) at previous visit = 1, then Q7a3b. IMAGLAC (Lacunar infarct(s)) should =1
